But I'm usually on time.

18
00:00:41,359 --> 00:00:46,799
Now, today we're talking about what would happen to the world if all the clocks stopped.

19
00:00:46,799 --> 00:00:49,599
It seems like that wouldn't worry you too much, Rob.

20
