Smartphones, computers, microwaves, bus stops.

24
00:00:57,039 --> 00:00:59,039
It's hard to get away from it.

25
00:00:59,039 --> 00:01:03,439
Did you know the word time is the most common noun in the English language,

26
00:01:03,439 --> 00:01:05,439
