27
00:01:05,439 --> 00:01:07,439
Oh, well, I didn't know that, Rob.

28
00:01:07,439 --> 00:01:09,439
But good timekeeping is extremely important.

29
00:01:09,439 --> 00:01:13,439
There are so many things to share during a day and so many deadlines to meet.

30
00:01:13,439 --> 00:01:15,439
Tick tock, tick tock.

31
